_Sans Serif_
[highlights](http://wearethebest.wordpress.com/2009/04/12/a-small-warning-to-
the-photo-thieves-of-the-world/) a Flickr group called [Indian Copyright
Laws](http://www.flickr.com/groups/indiancopyrights/pool/) that has sprung up
to showcase the work of individuals which have been used by different
mainstream media and websites without taking permission of the photographer, a
growing phenomenon in India.

